    "effect_entries": [
        {
            "effect": "Held\n:   Experience is split across two groups: Pok\u00e9mon who participated in battle, and Pok\u00e9mon holding this item.  Each Pok\u00e9mon earns experience as though it had battled alone, divided by the number of Pok\u00e9mon in its group, then divided by the number of groups. Pok\u00e9mon holding this item who also participated in battle effectively earn experience twice.\n\n    Fainted Pok\u00e9mon never earn experience, and empty groups are\nignored; thus, if a single Pok\u00e9mon is holding this item and the only Pok\u00e9mon who battled faints from explosion, the holder will gain full experience.",
            "language": {
                "name": "en",
                "url": "/api/v2/language/9/"
            },
            "short_effect": "Held: Half the experience from a battle is split between Pok\u00e9mon holding this item."
        }
    ],
    "flavor_text_entries": [
        {
            "language": {
                "name": "zh-Hans",
                "url": "/api/v2/language/12/"
            },
            "text": "\u6253\u5f00\u5f00\u5173\u540e\uff0c\n\u80fd\u8ba9\u540c\u884c\u7684\u6240\u6709\u5b9d\u53ef\u68a6\n\u83b7\u5f97\u7ecf\u9a8c\u503c\u7684\u88c5\u7f6e\u3002",
            "version_group": {
                "name": "ultra-sun-ultra-moon",
                "url": "/api/v2/version-group/18/"
            }
        },
        {
            "language": {
                "name": "ja",
                "url": "/api/v2/language/11/"
            },
            "text": "\u30b9\u30a4\u30c3\u30c1\u3092\u3000\u3044\u308c\u308b\u3068\n\u624b\u6301\u3061\u306e\u3000\u30dd\u30b1\u30e2\u30f3\u3000\u3059\u3079\u3066\u304c\n\u7d4c\u9a13\u5024\u3092\u3000\u3082\u3089\u3048\u308b\u3000\u88c5\u7f6e\u3002",
            "version_group": {
                "name": "ultra-sun-ultra-moon",
                "url": "/api/v2/version-group/18/"
            }
        },
        {
            "language": {
                "name": "en",
                "url": "/api/v2/language/9/"
            },
            "text": "Turning on this special device will allow all the\nPok\u00e9mon on your team to receive Exp. Points\nfrom battles.",
            "version_group": {
                "name": "ultra-sun-ultra-moon",
                "url": "/api/v2/version-group/18/"
            }
        },
        {
            "language": {
                "name": "it",
                "url": "/api/v2/language/8/"
            },
            "text": "Se attivato, tutti i Pok\u00e9mon della squadra ricevono\nPunti Esperienza dalla lotta anche se non vi hanno\npartecipato.",
            "version_group": {
                "name": "ultra-sun-ultra-moon",
                "url": "/api/v2/version-group/18/"
            }
        },
        {
            "language": {
                "name": "es",
                "url": "/api/v2/language/7/"
            },
            "text": "Al activar el dispositivo, todos los Pok\u00e9mon de\ntu equipo ganan Puntos de Experiencia tras los\ncombates, aunque no salgan a luchar.",
            "version_group": {
                "name": "ultra-sun-ultra-moon",
                "url": "/api/v2/version-group/18/"
            }
        },
        {
            "language": {
                "name": "de",
                "url": "/api/v2/language/6/"
            },
            "text": "Solange der EP-Teiler angeschaltet ist, erh\u00e4lt jedes\nTeam-Pok\u00e9mon nach einem Sieg Erfahrungspunkte.",
            "version_group": {
                "name": "ultra-sun-ultra-moon",
                "url": "/api/v2/version-group/18/"
            }
        },
        {
            "language": {
                "name": "fr",
